'''''First Empire''''' was a boxed campaign set planned to be released by [[West End Games]]. [[Pablo Hidalgo]] was involved, and in his own words:
:''"This was to be a boxed campaign set, a la [[The DarkStryder Campaign|DarkStryder]] or [[Lords of the Expanse]]. It never got off the planning stages. It only consisted of a few discussions between myself and [[Eric S. Trautmann|Eric Trautmann]]. I think [[Timothy Zahn|Tim Zahn]] and [[Michael A. Stackpole|Mike Stackpole]] shared some ideas with him as well. Since it was never pitched to [[Lucasfilm]] (as far as I know), I won't share any details on it. It had no title, but First Empire was my working suggestion. I think it's pretty cool, and maybe someday, it'll somehow be resurrected."''

